snippet.title: Johnny Depp assaulted Amber Heard on dozen occasions, UK High Court rules
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp assaulted Amber Heard on dozen occasions, UK High Court rules 
Johnny Depp assaulted his ex-wife Amber Heard on a dozen occasions, putting her in “fear for her life” during three of them, a High Court judge in England has ruled.
